lemma rt_fresher_def': "(rt\<^sub>1 \<sqsubseteq>\<^bsub>i\<^esub> rt\<^sub>2) = (nsqn\<^sub>r (the (rt\<^sub>1 i)) < nsqn\<^sub>r (the (rt\<^sub>2 i)) \<or> nsqn\<^sub>r (the (rt\<^sub>1 i)) = nsqn\<^sub>r (the (rt\<^sub>2 i)) \<and> \<pi>\<^sub>5 (the (rt\<^sub>2 i)) \<le> \<pi>\<^sub>5 (the (rt\<^sub>1 i)))"
